    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We wake up late in the lounge. I have a shower as my head is itchy and put on some colourful clothes for the first time in a few days. Corduroy pants and a blue t-shirt - but I’m on the fence. Then Jordan emerges in a great outfit and I’m inspired to try dressing myself again.",
            "link": null
          },
