      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We play a little spike ball game before leaving which is great fun, but severely lacking as there are only three of us. On the way back we stop at the Trasol (Trendy Sasol) that Kate describes as the place you stop at on the way after an affair to buy your wife an expensive guilty chocolate. We get some shortbread, jellybeans and chips.",
